graph TD
    A[User Login Request] --> B[Symfony Security]
    B --> C{User Exists?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401]
    C -->|Yes| E[Check Password]
    E -->|Invalid| D
    E -->|Valid| F[Generate JWT Token]
    F --> G[Check MFA Status]
    G -->|MFA Required| H[Send TOTP Challenge]
    G -->|MFA Not Required| M[Return Access Token]
    H --> I[User Enters TOTP Code]
    I --> J[Validate TOTP]
    J -->|Invalid| K[Return MFA Error]
    J -->|Valid| L[Generate MFA Token]
    L --> M
    M --> N[Store Session in Redis]
    N --> O[Return Success Response]
    
    P[Admin Panel - Vue.js] --> Q[API Gateway]
    Q --> R[Symfony Backend]
    R --> S[PostgreSQL Database]
    R --> T[Redis Cache]
    
    U[Google Authenticator] --> V[TOTP Generator]
    V --> I
    
    W[Rate Limiting] --> B
    X[Audit Logging] --> R
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style M fill:#c8e6c9
    style D fill:#ffcdd2
    style K fill:#ffcdd2
    style S fill:#fff3e0
    style T fill:#f3e5f5
